      • Public Sub AddCuboidMacroSetting(ByVal vntMasterMacroDetails As Variant)

        Public Sub AddCuboidMacroSetting(ByVal vntMasterMacroDetails As Variant)
        Details:

        '* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *
        '* Sub/Fn : AddCuboidMacroSetting
        '* Description : Add Macro entries in CUSTOM_CUBOID_MACRO range for Cuboid.
        '* Macro entries to be added are passed as paramter.
        '* Since Macro entries are derived from MASTER_CUBOID_MACRO i.e. Master Cuboid Macro settings,
        '* Formulas pointing to MASTER_CUBOID_MACROS are used to create Cuboid Macro Setting
        '* for Example, ..change this line FORMULA_CA_TemplateMode, FORMULA_CA_MacroName etc.
        '* By default Master Event Macros attached to Cuboid are Active.
        '* You can Deactivate it by navigating through SiteMap
        '* Created : 15-05-2013 16:31
        '* Modified: 15-05-2013 16:31
        '* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *
